[[div style="font-size:150%;text-align:center;"]]
+++ Book of Gnosis-repairers · Psalms
+++++ syzygy of brass and pearl
[[/div]]
[[div class="poem-xxx"]]
# Erst,  in the  forlorn murk phainoed ONTAMOVER
# HE encompassed ever-living fire
# Thence came forth with fever-rolling water
# Dense fog arose into never-guessing wonder[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# //Hearken, sounds of impalpable being//
# //is overflowed from dynamis  thinking//
# And the stark and ubiquitous meaning
# walked after lepid rhythme of forging
# Spirit just like pure and ethereal wind
# murmured inside deep, dark wooding[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# Aeons the elder gods rejoiced for vivace tempo
# Features of aretes appeared with pretty glow
# Praises blended in a chorus unto misty hollow
# Within odes fruit of Words betided and sanked
# unto mirage for photia-skia in terre's swallow[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# Suddenly, the whole Pleroma should
# be fallin into a silent, nebulous place
# Only ambiguity the precipitate could
# be seen to silhouette a slender trace[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# What a brassy  eidos, Oh
# could  form  thee  Serpent !
# Thy ineffablity mirroreth thy firm essence
#  which from [http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-kythera-creed interlligibility of dianoia's indentations]  [!----impressions ----]
# Peep in notches, so many  precise gear-like patterns
# Gaze at sequence, which performs like escapements [[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# What a pearl nous, Oh
# could morphe  thee  Serpent !
# Thy wit condenseth the purity as salt
# Big or tiny  gnosis cores regularly line on vault
# All of them  snuggle down in the becoming of brasen
# Such a harmonia between energico and  refinement [[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]  [!--unshake--]
# What a graceful  ergon, Oh
# could cast  thee  Serpent !
# Thy snell hypostasis  revealeth holy splendor
# Each action conformeth to entelecy number
# No material in phusis wherewith to exactly image
# any correct likeness of thy miraculous noumenon
# Cauze thou're the great present
# brought by the great PRESENCE[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# Thy had been clothing with vast light
# facing to the whole auroral Pleroma
# announcing thy spiritual oikodomia
# Logos the mesh is thy allegoric name of daena
# Nomos the ordre is thy all-inclusive exousia
# Who else would dare to glare at thy brights [!---burnish---]
# instant of grovellin in thy shadow as latreia
# But thou felt thyself being eclipsed  and inferior
# whencesoever thy  front was PRONOIA[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# With greatest respect bowed thou Serpent
# crawling unto FIRST CAUSE of narrativity
# Picked thy tail up in mouth gently
# thou obeyed the will of ALMIGHTY
# Hovered around HIS palm was thy hyparxis  [!----body---]
# Thou just like kuklos semeion so plain but plushy
# Fullness, unbroken, unity, perfection, eternity [[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# Afterwards, the great AGAPE
# who is above all over the Empyrean
# caressed the Paradigm whom sheweth as serpent
# whilst lifting thee up unto head of Aeons
# lifting thee up into center of Apeiron [!-- illimitation--]
# lifting thee up onto every dominion
# uttering Words to omniverse each section: [[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# //This creature which I give unto ye and the unborns will be//
# //a mentor for the erudite ecstasyer whom hath primacy//
# //Ophis the way wherewith sages find throne of mighty//
# //Within crowners that Paraclete'll shew supremacy// [[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# It came unto pass, as IMMACULÉ left off quething,
# that Serpent was put into pure and ethereal wind
# Thence NUMEN turned onto the super-celestial welkin
# whence tremendous majesty was remained and shined[[span class="a-brk"]]@@ @@[[/span]]
# Oh LA PROVIDENCE,  NECESSITE EN LUI-MÊME !
# Aeons dare not to glimpse your brightness whatever
# A long time passed they stood out chatting together
# They did not think they were anointed one however
# With triumphed from selves they did not need help
# They guardedly blessed Serpent with megalopsychia
# and turned back unto the  arkhe toposes thereafter
# But absent was young Sophia
[[/div]]


